The results indicated overall correlations between latency and accuracy of +0.66 for spelling tasks and +0.98 for phrase construction tasks across all five apps. Therefore, the two areas of accuracy and latency are positively correlated. The study also found that support could not be given for the mean latency calculations collected by Emmel (2013) and Graydon (2013).This data cannot be explained through the positive correlation between latency and accuracy due to other factors not addressed in this study.  Future studies should explore the variations between specific apps such as page and display construction to determine if these factors influence the latency and accuracy of phrase construction.},
